## this repository contains codes to extract clean text/speech from .cha files and also to count the various parameters such as grammatical errors, repetitions etc. ##

1. task1.py performs the task of cleaning the .cha files 
2. test script.txt contains the text from the .cha files which also contains a large number of unwanted texts. 
3. output1.text contains semi cleaned text. 
4. output2. text contains completely cleaned text. 
5. task2.py calculates the various parameters in the .cha files such as grammatical mistakes, repetitions etc. 


